<H1></H1>
<H1><CENTER>The Nobel Prize in Chemistry 1968</CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="chemistry-medalj.gif" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="93" NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3" ALIGN=bottom></CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>&quot;for the discovery of the reciprocal relations bearing
his name, which are fundamental for the thermodynamics of irreversible processes&quot;
</H3>
<BR>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5> <TR ALIGN=CENTER><TD NOWRAP> <IMG SRC="chemistry-1968-1.gif"
WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="198" ALIGN=bottom NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><BR>
