<HTML>
<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Chemistry 1966</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H1></H1>
<H1><CENTER>The Nobel Prize in Chemistry 1966</CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="chemistry-medalj.gif" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="93" NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3" ALIGN=bottom></CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>&quot;for his fundamental work concerning chemical bonds and
the electronic structure of molecules by the molecular orbital method&quot;
</H3>
<BR>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5> <TR ALIGN=CENTER> <TD NOWRAP><IMG SRC="chemistry-1966-1.gif"
WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="198" ALIGN=bottom NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"> <BR>
<BR>
<B>Robert S. Mulliken</B><BR>
<BR>
USA<BR>
<BR>
University of Chicago<BR>
Chicago, IL, USA<BR>
<BR>
1896 - 1986<BR>
