<HTML>
<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Literature 1962</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H1><CENTER>The Nobel Prize in Literature 1962</CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="literature-medalj.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> </CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>&quot;for his realistic and imaginative writings, combining
as they do sympathetic humour and keen social perception&quot;

</H3>
