<BODY>
<H1><CENTER>The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 1957</CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="medicine-medalj.gif" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="93" NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>&quot;for his discoveries relating to synthetic compounds that
inhibit the action of certain body substances, and especially their action
on the vascular system and the skeletal muscles&quot;
</H3>
<BR>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5> <TR ALIGN=CENTER> <TD NOWRAP> <IMG SRC="medicine-1957-1.gif"
WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="198" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" ALIGN="BOTTOM"><BR>
