<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Physics 1945</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H1></H1>
<H1><CENTER>The Nobel Prize in Physics 1945</CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="physics-medalj.gif" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="93" ALIGN=bottom
NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>&quot;for the discovery of the Exclusion Principle, also called
the Pauli Principle&quot;</CENTER>
</H3>
<P><CENTER><BR>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5> <TR ALIGN=CENTER> <TD NOWRAP> <IMG SRC="physics-1945-1.gif"
WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="198" ALIGN=bottom NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><BR>
<BR>
<B>Wolfgang Pauli</B><BR>
<BR>
Austria<BR>
<BR>
Princeton University<BR>
Princeton, NJ, USA<BR>
<BR>
1900 - 1958<BR>
<BR>
</TD> </TR> </TABLE> <BR>
