</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="chemistry-medalj.gif" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="93" NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3" ALIGN=bottom></CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>&quot;for his research and inventions in agricultural and nutrition
chemistry, especially for his fodder preservation method&quot;
</H3>
