<H1><CENTER>The Nobel Prize in Literature 1945</CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="literature-medalj.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> </CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>&quot;for her lyric poetry which, inspired by powerful emotions,
has made her name a symbol of the idealistic aspirations of the entire Latin
American world&quot;
</H3>
<BR>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5> <TR ALIGN=CENTER> <TD NOWRAP> <IMG SRC="literature-1945-1.gif"
WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="198" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><BR>
