<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Physiology or Medicine 1943 (awarded 1944)</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H1><CENTER>The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 1943</CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="medicine-medalj.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT=
"93" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>&quot;for his discovery of vitamin K&quot;
</H3>
<BR>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5> <TR ALIGN=CENTER> <TD NOWRAP> <IMG SRC="medicine-1943-1.gif"
ALIGN="BOTTOM" WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="198" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><BR>
<BR>
<B>Henrik Carl Peter Dam</B><BR>
<BR>
Denmark<BR>
<BR>
Polytechnic Institute<BR>
Copenhagen, Denmark<BR>
<BR>
1895 - 1976<BR>
<BR>
</TD> </TR> </TABLE> </CENTER>
<H3><CENTER><BR>
&quot;for his discovery of the chemical nature of vitamin K&quot;
</H3>
<BR>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5> <TR ALIGN=CENTER> <TD NOWRAP><IMG SRC="medicine-1943-2.gif"
ALIGN="BOTTOM" WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="198" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><BR>
<BR>
<B>Edward Adelbert Doisy</B><BR>
<BR>
USA<BR>
<BR>
Saint Louis University<BR>
St. Louis, MO, USA<BR>
<BR>
1893 - 1986<BR>
<BR>
</TD> </TR> </TABLE> <BR>
