</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H1><CENTER>The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 1935</CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="medicine-medalj.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> </CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>&quot;for his discovery of the organizer effect in embryonic
development&quot;
</H3>
<BR>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5> <TR ALIGN=CENTER> <TD NOWRAP> <IMG SRC="medicine-1935-1.gif"
ALIGN="BOTTOM" WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="198" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><BR>
<BR>
<B>Hans Spemann</B><BR>
<BR>
Germany<BR>
<BR>
University of Freiburg im Breisgau<BR>
Freiburg, Germany<BR>
<BR>
1869 - 1941<BR>
<BR>
</TD> </TR> </TABLE> <BR>
