<BODY>
<H1></H1>
<H1><CENTER>The Nobel Prize in Physics 1932</CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="physics-medalj.gif" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="93" ALIGN=bottom
NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>&quot;for the creation of quantum mechanics, the application
of which has, inter alia, led to the discovery of the allotropic forms of
hydrogen&quot;</CENTER>
</H3>
<P><CENTER><BR>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5> <TR ALIGN=CENTER> <TD NOWRAP> <IMG SRC="physics-1932-1.gif"
WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="198" ALIGN=bottom NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><BR>
