<H1></H1>
<H1><CENTER>The Nobel Prize in Physics 1922</CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="physics-medalj.gif" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="93" ALIGN=bottom
NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>&quot;for his services in the investigation of the structure
of atoms and of the radiation emanating from them&quot;</CENTER>
</H3>
<P><CENTER><BR>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5> <TR ALIGN=CENTER> <TD NOWRAP> <IMG SRC="physics-1922-1.gif"
WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="198" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B>Niels Bohr</B><BR>
<BR>
Denmark<BR>
<BR>
Copenhagen University<BR>
Copenhagen, Denmark<BR>
<BR>
1885 - 1962<BR>
<BR>
</TD> </TR> </TABLE> <BR>
