</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="medicine-medalj.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT=
"93" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>&quot;for his discovery relating to the production of heat in
the muscle&quot;
</H3>
<BR>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5> <TR ALIGN=CENTER> <TD NOWRAP> <IMG SRC="medicine-1922-1.gif"
