London University<BR>
London, Great Britain<BR>
<BR>
1886 - 1977<BR>
<BR>
</TD> </TR> </TABLE> </CENTER>
<H3><CENTER><BR>
<BR>
&quot;for his discovery of the fixed relationship between the consumption
of oxygen and the metabolism of lactic acid in the muscle&quot;
