    <TITLE>Physics 1909</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H1></H1>
<H1><CENTER>The Nobel Prize in Physics 1909</CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="physics-medalj.gif" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="93" ALIGN=bottom
NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></CENTER>
<H3><CENTER>&quot;in recognition of their contributions to the development
of wireless telegraphy&quot;</CENTER>
</H3>
<P><CENTER><BR>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5> <TR ALIGN=CENTER> <TD NOWRAP WIDTH=50%> <IMG SRC=
"physics-1909-1.gif" WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="198" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" ALIGN=
bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B>Guglielmo Marconi</B><BR>
<BR>
Italy<BR>
<BR>
Marconi Wireless Telegraph Co. Ltd.<BR>
London, Great Britain<BR>
<BR>
1874 - 1937<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
</TD> <TD NOWRAP WIDTH=50%> <IMG SRC="physics-1909-2.gif" WIDTH="140" HEIGHT=
"198" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B>Carl Ferdinand Braun</B><BR>
<BR>
Germany<BR>
<BR>
Strasbourg University<BR>
Alsace (then Germany)<BR>
<BR>
1850 - 1918<BR>
<BR>
</TD> </TR> </TABLE> <BR>
