<P><IMG SRC="physics-medalj.gif" WIDTH="93" HEIGHT="93" ALIGN=bottom NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"></CENTER>

<H3><CENTER>&quot;in recognition of the extraordinary service they rendered
by their researches into the influence of magnetism upon radiation phenomena&quot;</CENTER>
</H3>
<P><CENTER><BR>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5> <TR ALIGN=CENTER> <TD NOWRAP> <IMG SRC="physics-1902-1.gif"
WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="198" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B>Hendrik Antoon Lorentz</B><BR>
<BR>
the Netherlands<BR>
<BR>
Leyden University<BR>
Leyden, the Netherlands<BR>
<BR>
1853 - 1928<BR>
<BR>
</TD> <TD NOWRAP> <IMG SRC="physics-1902-2.gif" WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="198"
NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B>Pieter Zeeman</B><BR>
<BR>
the Netherlands<BR>
<BR>
Amsterdam University<BR>
Amsterdam, the Netherlands<BR>
<BR>
1865 - 1943<BR>
<BR>
</TD> </TR> </TABLE> <BR>
