    <TITLE>The Nobel Committee</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<HR>
<H1>The Nobel Committee 1997</H1>
<HR>The Nobel Committee consists of five members and the secretary
of the Nobel Assembly. The members are elected for a period of three 
years. Each year, ten associate members are elected for a term running 
from March until October. The Nobel Committee is the working body of the 
Nobel Assembly.<HR>
<BR>
