</HEAD>
<BODY>

<P><HR>
<H1> Nobel Laureate Revisiting Lectures</H1>
<HR>Since 1980 one or several previous Nobel Laureates in Physiology or
Medicine are invited to return to Stockholm to give a Nobel Laureate
Revisiting Lecture at the Karolinska Institute. The Laureates also meet
with the Medical Nobel Committee for informal discussions of recent developments
within the scientific area defined by the prize. <BR>
<BR>
