<DOCHDR>
http://www.nobel.se:80/essays/curie/curie-text.html 130.237.132.126 19970115094815 text/html 56260
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Enterprise/2.0c
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 09:49:48 GMT
Last-modified: Fri, 29 Nov 1996 09:27:43 GMT
