<DOCNO>WT05-B10-361</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA061-000339-B004-49</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.nobel.se:80/essays/french-lit/poster4.html 130.237.132.126 19970115094910 text/html 3552
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Enterprise/2.0c
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 09:51:10 GMT
Last-modified: Thu, 05 Dec 1996 10:04:19 GMT
Content-length: 3369
Content-type: text/html
