<DOCOLDNO>IA061-000339-B005-218</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.nobel.se:80/laureates/literature-1996-press.html 130.237.132.126 19970115095624 text/html 9368
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Enterprise/2.0c
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 09:58:31 GMT
Last-modified: Wed, 27 Nov 1996 21:53:52 GMT
