Krynski and Robert A. Maguire. Princeton Univ. Press 1981.
<li><i>People on a Bridge.</i> Introd. and transl. By Adam Czerniawski.  Forest Books 1990.
<li><i>View with a Grain of Sand.</i>  Selected poems. Harcourt Brace & Company 1995.
</ul>

<p>
<b>Selections from her poetry appear in the following collections:</b>
<ul>
<li><i>Polish Writing Today.</i>  Ed. by C. Wieniewska.  1967.
<li><i>The Burning Forest.  Modern Polish Poetry.</i>  Ed. and transl. by Adam
Czerniawski.  Bloodaxe Books 1988.
<li><i>Ariadne's Thread:  Polish Women Poets.</i> Ed. and transl. by Susan Bassnett
and Piotr   Kuhiwczak.  1988.
</ul>
<h3>Literature</h3>
<ul>
<li>E. Balcerzan, <i>Kregi wtajemniczenia,</i> Wydawnictwo Literackie 1982.
<li>J. Kwiatkowski, Swiat wsr&oacute;d nie-swiat&oacute;w. In: Jerzy Kwiatkowski, <i>Remont
pegaz&oacute;w.</i> Czytelnik 1969.
<li><i>The Mature Laurel. Essays on Modern Polish Poetry.</i> Ed. by Adam Czerniawski.
Seren Books 1991.
<li>R. Matuszewski, <i>Z bliska. Szkice literackie.</i> Wydawnictwo Literackie 1981.
<li>S. Melkowski, <i>R&oacute;wiesnicy i bracia starsi.</i> Czytelnik 1980.
<li>A. Sandauer, Pogodzona z historia. In: <i>Poeci czterech pokolen</i>. Wydawnictwo
Literackie 1977.
</ul>
</body>
