of Northern Ireland. </I>Dufour 1992<BR>
Harold Bloom (ed.), <I>Seamus Heaney. </I>Chelsea House 1986<BR>
Thomas Foster, <I>Seamus Heaney. </I>Twayne 1989<BR>
