<BODY>
<H2><CENTER>JOSEPH ROTBLAT</CENTER>
</H2>
<IMG SRC="peace-1995-1.gif" ALIGN=left VSPACE=5 HSPACE=10 WIDTH=
"140" HEIGHT="198" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3">
<h3>Curriculum Vitae</H3>
Born - Warsaw, 4 November 1908 (British citizen since 1946)<BR>
Educated at the Free University of Poland and the University of Warsaw,
Poland<BR>
